Digital Twin Blueprint

This description should be updated with:
* Documentation and videos available at https://community.vantiq.com/
* List of plugins

Centrak RTLS - App that connects to RTLS data from CENTRAL
ContactTracing - Add contact tracing into accelerator, used in conjunction with RTLS data
GiConnectThermal - App to connect GiConnect Thermnal Camera into accelerator
HandSantizer - Notify maintenace when levels drop below threshold
Physical Distance - Notify Security if crowd is forming for extended period of time
Restriced Space - Notify security if RTLS data appears in restriced area
